DOC.LD:
   After several months of public meetings, focus groups and board work
sessions, Supt. Percy Clark's initiative had evolved and expanded to
include reopening a closed campus to accommodate elementary and middle
school students; creating a math and sciences magnet at one middle school;
building a new elementary school in the northwest section of the district;
and drawing new attendance zone maps.
